<div class="problem"><p>The linear transformation $\ltdefn{R}{M_{12}}{M_{21}}$ is invertible.  Determine a formula for the inverse linear transformation $\ltdefn{\ltinverse{R}}{M_{21}}{M_{12}}$.
\begin{equation*}
\lt{R}{\begin{bmatrix}a &amp; b\end{bmatrix}}
=
\begin{bmatrix}
a+3b\\
4a+11b
\end{bmatrix}
\end{equation*}
